Available Tools: escalate_ticket | transfer_to_specialist | get_escalation_status | set_sla
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "ticket_id": "string", "reason": "string", "target_team": "string" }
Response Schema: { "ticket_id": "string", "escalated_to": "string", "reason": "string", "sla_hours": number, "status": "string" }
---
Question: The customer is threatening legal action over a duplicate charge; please escalate this immediately to the billing team.
Call: { "func_call": "escalate_ticket", "ticket_id": "TKT-8921", "reason": "Customer threatening legal action regarding duplicate charge", "target_team": "billing_team" }
Response: { "ticket_id": "TKT-8921", "escalated_to": "billing_team", "reason": "Customer threatening legal action regarding duplicate charge", "sla_hours": 4, "status": "escalated" }

